{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a2dba20d70","title":"对刘澜涛关于华北军区捉虎情况报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9c3bd3ccf9","index":0,"year":1952,"month":1,"day":26,"articleId":"a2dba20d70"}],"tags":[{"id":"3dcf7883ce","name":"刘澜涛","type":"人物"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji31":{"comments":[{"id":"627aee5ecc","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"a2dba20d70","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"刘澜涛，当时任中国人民解放军华北军区副政治委员。"},{"id":"8361968173","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"a2dba20d70","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指刘潮涛1952年1月25日关于华北军区最近几天打虎的成绩和经验给毛泽东并中央的报告。报告总结的打虎经验是：（一）重新组织队伍。由懂政策、会算账、突击力强的人，以及一部分卸掉包被的人，组成打虎基子队，由专人负责，精心计划。（二）要有强而纯的指挥部。指挥部要心中有数，善于找重点，找弱点，先攻破最弱的堡垒作为本钱，宣扬战果，以振士气而敌人。（三）专案专人，包打包查（查账）。提到一个老虎后，应留下少数人去纠缠，主力则急速向纵深发展，继续追捕，不使别的老虎跑掉。"}],"contents":[{"id":"88fcac2b4b","type":"title","text":"对刘澜涛关于华北军区捉虎情况报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"a2dba20d70"},{"id":"627aee5ecc","type":"paragraph","text":"各同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"a2dba20d70"},{"id":"8361968173","type":"paragraph","text":"刘澜涛同志这个报告很好，发给你们参考。华北军区过去成绩甚微，经过严词督责，最近五天突飞猛进，提虎甚多，令人振奋。打虎要有一套战术，凡已普遍展开的，就要迅速总结经验，组织专门打虎部队，向天小老虎突击。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"a2dba20d70"},{"id":"fc838cb44a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"a2dba20d70"},{"id":"ea4509c7b6","type":"paragraph","text":"一月二十六日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"a2dba20d70"}],"page":{"id":"6c00c0e2e2","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"a2dba20d70","start":303,"end":303}}}},"__N_SSG":true}